tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    accessibility_needs BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE demographics (
    demographic_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID REFERENCES users(user_id),
    income DECIMAL(10,2),
    education_level VARCHAR(50),
    race VARCHAR(50),
    accessibility_score INT
);

CREATE TABLE UserPreferences (
    preference_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID REFERENCES Users(user_id),
    accessibility_mode BOOLEAN,
    color_theme STRING,
    font_size INT
);

CREATE TABLE UserDemographics (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR,
    ethnicity VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE ApplicationLogs (
    log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    log_description VARCHAR,
    log_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE ARFeatures (
    feature_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    feature_name VARCHAR,
    feature_description VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE UserFeedback (
    feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    feedback_rating INT
)

CREATE TABLE accessibility_features (
  feature_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  feature_name STRING,
  feature_description STRING
)

CREATE TABLE user_demographics (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_name STRING,
  age INT,
  gender STRING,
  ethnicity STRING
)

CREATE TABLE ar_applications (
  app_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  app_name STRING,
  app_category STRING,
  accessibility_feature_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE user_preferences (
  user_id INT,
  app_id INT,
  preference_type STRING
)

CREATE TABLE demographics_history (
  user_id INT,
  date DATE,
  action_taken STRING
)
